tool : https://theintern.github.io/

get chrome driver: http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html?path=2.24/

install:
npm install --save-dev intern


samples:
https://github.com/theintern/intern-examples

userguide:
https://theintern.github.io/intern/#what-is-intern

command reference:
https://theintern.github.io/leadfoot/module-leadfoot_Command.html

execute :


1. run chromedriver-run.cmd
2. make 'screenshot' folder on root folder
3. run command below
node_modules\.bin\intern-runner config=tests\intern

capture configuration:
edit consts.js
  set capture: true
  set capturePath: 'screenshot' // from project root
